overview: Swiss conductor Joel Mathias Jenny leads the Les Orpheistes Festival Orchestra and Bulgarian violinist Mario Hossen in this celebratory evening of beautiful classical music, featuring the world premiere of Walter Baer's "Winter Music." Other tracks include Antonio Vivaldi's "Winter," Johannes Brahms's "Hungarian Dance No. 5," Piotr Tchaikovsky's "Elegia," Niccol√≤ Paganini's "I Palpiti" and Pablo de Sarasate's "Zigeunerweisen."
title: Orpheistes Festival Orchestra Live
